-*- org -*-

* Requirements
-----------------

Install both the runtime and the development libraries for:

OCaml (see http://caml.inria.fr/download.en.html)
make

Then simply type
 ./configure
 make depend
 make


* Linux distributions
-----------------------

** Ubuntu

sudo apt-get ocaml

** gentoo

emerge ocaml

* Godi
------------

The simplest way to install the prerequisites needed by this software is
via the Godi package manager for OCaml. Download godi from

  http://godi.ocaml-programming.de/

Follow installation instructions.  Then issue the commands:

  godi_console perform -build godi-ocaml-all



